---
---

<div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label reveal">What makes me different</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading reveal reveal-delay-1">
        Not your average <span class="highlight">developer</span>.
    </h2>

    <div class="traits-list">
        <div class="trait-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="trait-icon">&#9881;</div>
            <div class="trait-content">
                <h3>AI-Native Builder</h3>
                <p>I don't just use AI &mdash; I build with it, ship with it, and think in agentic workflows. Every project is an AI collaboration.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="trait-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="trait-icon">&#9812;</div>
            <div class="trait-content">
                <h3>Team-builder</h3>
                <p>Always involved in building truly great teams. Coached developers, recruited talent, unified fragmented departments.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="trait-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="trait-icon">&#128027;</div>
            <div class="trait-content">
                <h3>Debugger</h3>
                <p>Loves the kind of complex troubleshooting that makes other people reach for the rewrite button.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="trait-item reveal reveal-delay-4">
            <div class="trait-icon">&#9875;</div>
            <div class="trait-content">
                <h3>"Legacy Diver"</h3>
                <p>Has a track record of rescuing legacy codebases when everyone else wanted to rewrite from scratch.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .traits-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 24px;
    }

    .trait-item {
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 24px;
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .trait-item:hover {
        border-color: var(--purple-dim);
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--purple-glow);
    }

    .trait-icon {
        width: 48px;
        height: 48px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: var(--purple-glow-strong);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 22px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .trait-content h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .trait-content p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-dim);
    }

    @media print {
        .traits-list {
            display: grid !important;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .trait-item { padding: 8px; border-radius: 6px; gap: 10px; }
        .trait-item:hover { box-shadow: none; }
        .trait-content h3 { font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        .trait-content p { font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.3; }
        .trait-icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 6px; }
    }
</style>
